ZH: 我们的租金每个月都会涨价。
EN: Our rent goes up every month.

ZH: 他们不得不降低租金，吸引更多租户。
EN: They had to lower the rent to attract more tenants.

ZH: 这个城市的租金水平非常高。
EN: The rent levels in this city are very high.

ZH: 我们的租金包括水电费。
EN: Our rent includes utilities.

ZH: 每个月底都要交一次租金。
EN: Rent is due at the end of each month.

ZH: 这个区域的租金相对便宜。
EN: The rent in this area is relatively cheap.

ZH: 我们将提高租金，以反映市场价格。
EN: We will raise the rent to reflect market prices.

ZH: 最近，我听说了一些关于提高租金的传言。
EN: I heard rumors recently about raising the rent.

ZH: 每个季度都要支付一次租金。
EN: Rent is due every quarter.

ZH: 我们增加了一些设施以提高租金。
EN: We added some amenities to increase the rent.

ZH: 我们租金是每周支付的。
EN: Our rent is paid weekly.

ZH: 他们签订了一份长期租金协议。
EN: They signed a long-term lease agreement.

ZH: 我们不得不削减开支, 因为租金太高了。
EN: We had to cut expenses because the rent was too high.

ZH: 在城市中心，租金比郊区更高。
EN: In the city center, rent is higher than in the suburbs.

ZH: 我们的租金包括楼下的停车位。
EN: Our rent includes a parking space downstairs.

ZH: 不幸的是，他们无法负担这个地区的租金。
EN: Unfortunately, they couldn't afford the rent in this area.

ZH: 我们的租金合同还剩下几个月。
EN: Our lease contract has a few months left.

ZH: 房东提醒我们要按时支付租金。
EN: The landlord reminded us to pay the rent on time.

ZH: 如果不支付租金，他们就会被驱逐出去。
EN: They will be evicted if they don't pay the rent.

ZH: 他们决定取消租金上涨的计划。
EN: They decided to cancel the plan to raise the rent.
